Source files ported (Java → TypeScript):
  - LoadingIndicatorAnimatorDelegate.java → src/core/animator.ts
  - LoadingIndicatorDrawingDelegate.java  → src/core/shapes.ts, src/core/renderer.ts
  - LoadingIndicatorSpec.java             → (constants in animator.ts)
  - LoadingIndicator.java                 → (component wrappers)

Changes made:
  - Translated from Java/Android to TypeScript/Web Canvas API
  - Replaced Android SpringAnimation with equivalent spring physics simulation
  - Replaced AndroidX Morph/RoundedPolygon with SVG path parsing and point-based
    linear interpolation
  - Replaced Android Canvas drawing with HTML Canvas 2D API
  - Created framework-specific wrappers for React, Svelte 5, and Vue 3

